---
// Form, şimdilik Formspree placeholder endpoint’i kullanıyor.
// Sonradan kendi n8n webhook’umuza bağlanabilir (POST -> Telegram bildirim).
---

<section id="iletisim" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-ink text-paper relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-10"></div>

  <div class="container-wide relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="label mb-4 text-paper/50">İletişim</p>
        <h2 class="display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight">
          1 saat ayırın.<br />
          <span class="text-paper/50 italic">Geri kalanını biz çözeriz.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-paper/70 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Aşağıdaki formu doldurun ya da doğrudan e-posta ile yazın. 24 saat içinde 15 dakikalık tanışma görüşmesi için dönüş yaparız.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-4 text-sm">
          <a
            href="mailto:merhaba@postfabrica.co"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-paper/80 hover:text-paper transition-colors"
          >
            <span class="size-9 rounded-full bg-paper/10 grid place-items-center text-paper/70">@</span>
            <span class="font-mono">merhaba@postfabrica.co</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://t.me/postfabrica"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-paper/80 hover:text-paper transition-colors"
          >
            <span class="size-9 rounded-full bg-paper/10 grid place-items-center text-paper/70">✈</span>
            <span class="font-mono">@postfabrica (Telegram)</span>
          </a>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-paper/60">
            <span class="size-9 rounded-full bg-paper/10 grid place-items-center text-paper/60">⌖</span>
            <span class="font-mono">İstanbul · Türkiye</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <form
          action="https://formspree.io/f/PLACEHOLDER"
          method="POST"
          class="bg-paper text-ink rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5"
          id="lead-form"
        >
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="label block mb-2">Ad Soyad</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="name"
                name="name"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
                placeholder="Adınız Soyadınız"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="company" class="label block mb-2">Şirket</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="company"
                name="company"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
                placeholder="Şirket adı"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="label block mb-2">E-posta</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
                placeholder="ornek@sirket.com"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="label block mb-2">Telefon <span class="text-muted">(opsiyonel)</span></label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                id="phone"
                name="phone"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
                placeholder="+90 ..."
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="sector" class="label block mb-2">Sektör</label>
            <select
              id="sector"
              name="sector"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              <option value="">Seçiniz</option>
              <option>Toptan / e-ticaret dağıtım</option>
              <option>Küçük üretim / atölye</option>
              <option>Ajans / kreatif stüdyo</option>
              <option>Muhasebe / danışmanlık bürosu</option>
              <option>Lojistik / nakliye</option>
              <option>Diğer</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="message" class="label block mb-2">Mevcut durumunuz <span class="text-muted">(3 cümle yeter)</span></label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="4"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-cream/30 focus:bg-paper focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors text-sm resize-none"
              placeholder="Örn: WhatsApp’tan gelen siparişleri Excel’e elle yazıyoruz, ERP’ye haftada bir toplu giriyoruz. 6 kişiyiz, hata çok oluyor."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              id="consent"
              name="consent"
              required
              class="mt-1 size-4 rounded border-line text-ink focus:ring-ink"
            />
            <label for="consent" class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
              İletişim bilgilerimden Postfabrica’nın benimle iletişime geçmesini kabul ediyorum. Verilerim üçüncü taraflarla paylaşılmaz.
            </label>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn-primary w-full justify-center py-3"
          >
            15 dakikalık tanışma görüşmesi için gönder
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </button>

          <p class="text-[11px] text-muted text-center font-mono">
            Spam yok. Sadece gerçek bir insan mesajı var.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
